## **[INDEX.HTML - HOMEPAGE]**

### **1. PURPOSE**
Landing page after login. Displays all available movies across three categories (Now Showing, Advance Ticket Selling, Coming Soon). Users can search for movies, browse collections, and click to book tickets.

### **2. UI ELEMENTS**

| Element | Function |
|---------|----------|
| **Header (cs-header)** | Navigation bar with CineSpot logo, menu links, and profile dropdown |
| **Search Bar** | Real-time movie search across all categories with "no results" message |
| **Movie Carousels (3 sections)** | Infinite-loop carousels for Now Showing, Advance, Coming Soon with prev/next buttons |
| **Movie Cards** | Clickable poster cards with title, overlay text, and hover effects |
| **Profile Dropdown** | Shows user name, email, member since, tickets booked; links to profile, history, settings, logout |
| **Navigation Links** | Now Showing, Cinemas, Advance Ticket Selling, Coming Soon |

### **3. USER INTERACTIONS**

**Movie Search:**
- User types in search box → filters movies from all 3 sections → highlights matching text → shows/hides "no results"
- `filterAndRebuild()` function rebuilds carousels with filtered movies with `isSearchMode=true` (no duplication)

**Carousel Navigation:**
- Click **prev/next buttons** → moves carousel by one card width (cardWidth + 32px gap)
- When at last card → jumps to clone of first card → transitions seamlessly to beginning
- When at first card → jumps to clone of last card → infinite loop maintained

**Movie Selection:**
- Click poster → event listener on `.movie-card` captures click
- Prevents multiple rapid clicks with `clicked` class flag
- Stores `movieId` in `localStorage['selectedMovie']`
- Stores full movie object in `sessionStorage['movieSelection']`
- Navigates to movie-details.html

**Profile Dropdown:**
- Click on profile container → toggles `.show` class on dropdown
- Click outside dropdown → removes `.show` class
- Click "Sign Out" → removes `cinespot_logged_in` from localStorage → redirects to login.html

### **4. DATA FLOW**

**Data Stored:**
- `localStorage['cinespot_logged_in']` - login status flag
- `localStorage['cinespot_user']` - user object (name, email, password, tickets, member since)
- `localStorage['selectedMovie']` - selected movie ID
- `sessionStorage['movieSelection']` - full movie object (title, image, genre, director, cast, description, rating, cinema)

**Data Retrieved:**
- Profile data from `localStorage['cinespot_user']` populates header ("Hi, [name]")
- Movie `carouselData` object contains all 11 movies across 3 categories
- Movies normalized by ID: title → lowercase, spaces to hyphens, special chars removed

**Data Transformation:**
- Movie title → normalized ID (e.g., "The Batman" → "the-batman")
- Movies duplicated 10+ times in carousel for infinite loop effect
- First card cloned at end, last card cloned at beginning
- Original cards marked with `data-original="true"` attribute

### **5. NAVIGATION FLOW**

**Entry:** User comes from login.html (after authentication)
**Current:** Home page showing all movies
**Exit Options:**
- Click movie poster → `movie-details.html?id=[movieId]`
- Click "Now Showing" nav link → now-showing.html (simplified single-section view)
- Click "Advance Ticket Selling" nav link → advance-ticket-selling.html
- Click "Coming Soon" nav link → coming-soon.html
- Click "Cinemas" nav link → cinemas.html
- Click "View Profile" in dropdown → profile.html
- Click "Booking History" in dropdown → booking-history.html
- Click "Account Settings" in dropdown → account-settings.html

